b'When it comes to flying you to more destinations, with more options and a seamless experience, our new partnership with @americanair gets straight A\xe2\x80\x99s. Check the link in our bio for more.'

b'To promote physical distancing, we\xe2\x80\x99re blocking middle seats thru 9/8 on our larger planes (and most aisle seats on our smaller planes), except for those traveling together. Check the link in our bio to learn more.'

b'On this day in 1865, news of emancipation finally reached the last enslaved Black Americans denied their humanity under chattel slavery. 155 years later, we celebrate the holiday amid calls for equity for all Black Americans \xe2\x80\x94 an inspiring moment of humanity worth celebrating through reflection, education, and advocacy. #Juneteenth #BlackLivesMatter'

b'Safety from the Ground Up starts with a face covering from the chin up. JetBlue now requires all travelers to wear a face covering over their nose and mouth during check-in, boarding and in flight.'
b'See how we\xe2\x80\x99re putting our commitment to safety from the ground up into action as JetBlue President and COO Joanna Geraghty invites you to tag along as she flies from New York to Boston.'

b"After today's landmark decision, there\xe2\x80\x99s never been a better time to remind ourselves that love is love. :red_heart_selector::orange_heart::yellow_heart::green_heart::blue_heart::purple_heart::black_heart::brown_heart: #NonstopPride"

b"Now extended! To promote physical distancing on board, we're blocking middle seats for purchase on our larger aircraft, and most aisle seats on our smaller aircraft, for those not traveling together through July 31st. Check the link in our bio to learn more."

b'Our favorite simple machine? The inclined plane. Because we\xe2\x80\x99re plane-inclined. Grab your kids and join General Manager Anthony for a lesson in the simple machines that help an airport run smoothly. Check it out at the link in our bio.'
b'At JetBlue, we stand together against racism.'

b'We\xe2\x80\x99ve always prided ourselves on having \xe2\x80\x9cservice with a smile.\xe2\x80\x9d But these days it\xe2\x80\x99s more like \xe2\x80\x9cservice with a smize.\xe2\x80\x9d Thank you to all of our incredible inflight crewmembers, for staying fly no matter what. Happy International Flight Attendants\xe2\x80\x99 Day!'

b'When it comes to health and safety, we\xe2\x80\x99ve got your (seat)back with Safety from the Ground Up. Swipe through to see what we\xe2\x80\x99re doing for our customers (that\xe2\x80\x99s you!) and crewmembers on the ground and in the sky. Head to the link in our bio for all the deets.'

b'To promote physical distancing on board, we\xe2\x80\x99re blocking middle seats for purchase on our larger aircraft, and most aisle seats on our smaller aircraft, for those not traveling together through July 6th. Check the link in bio to learn more.'

b'WFH (Wander From Home) and add some Costa Rican chill to your week with our @inscape live meditation session at @ 11 a.m. EDT today. Can\xe2\x80\x99t make it? Check out our Story for our free Costa Rica relaxation playlist.'

b'You might water-fall in love when you WFH (Wander From Home) with us to Costa Rica. With help from our inflight partners, we\xe2\x80\x99ve set our sites on the best beats, retreats and adventurous feats the country has to offer. Head to the link in our bio and start exploring.'

b'Healthy crewmembers. Clean air and surfaces. More space and fewer touchpoints. Travel flexibility. With our Safety from the Ground Up program, we\xe2\x80\x99re going above and beyond to keep our customers and crewmembers safe and well. Check out the link in our bio to learn more.'

b'Knowing where you\xe2\x80\x99re going is a pretty instrumental part of flying. Today on JetBlue Jr., Captain Luis has a kid-friendly lesson on navigating navigation\xe2\x80\x94from the instruments we use, to the directions on a compass. Check it out at the link in our bio.'

b'Get ready to sit back, relax and enjoy @inscape live. Today @ 11am we\xe2\x80\x99re helping you WFH (Wander From Home) to Mexico in real time with a live meditation session on our Instagram. Tune in for a brief escape and check out our Story for our full Mexico meditation playlist.'

b'Time to get up and Mexi-go! WFH (Wander From Home) with us through the wonders of Mexico. You\xe2\x80\x99ll dive into our favorite city sites, try dishes to fly for and take a break to meditate. All courtesy of our inflight partners. Fly over to the link in our bio to start wandering.'

b'Know a healthcare worker (or 10!) that deserves some R&R? Of course you do. Doctors, nurses, respiratory therapists, EMTs, orderlies, administrators, social workers...the list goes on. Nominate a healthcare hero and they could receive roundtrip flights for 2. Click the link in bio. #JetBlueHealthcareHero Recipient pays flight taxes & fees.'

b'For #NationalTourismDay, we wanted to take a moment to recognize the tourists of New York, past and future. Yes, you block the sidewalk. No, you don\xe2\x80\x99t understand how the subway works. And strangely, many of you decide to eat pizza with a knife and fork. We miss all of that and can\xe2\x80\x99t wait to see you again.'

b'Tomorrow at 7pm, our special I:red_heart:NY, NYPD and FDNY planes are joining NYC\xe2\x80\x99s #ClapBecauseWeCare with a flyover salute for our hometown healthcare heroes and first responders. So, keep your eyes up, and keep a healthy distance from others while watching.'

b'Across the country, healthcare workers have earned our love, our gratitude and some serious R&R. To thank them, we\xe2\x80\x99re giving away 100,000 pairs of roundtrip flights. Nominate YOUR #JetBlueHealthcareHero and they could receive roundtrip flights for 2. Click link in bio. Recipient pays flight taxes & fees.'

b'How does the \xe2\x80\x9cJet\xe2\x80\x9d part of JetBlue work? Glad you asked. This week on JetBlue Jr., join Captain Samer for a high-speed lesson in the physics of flight for kids\xe2\x80\x94and the finer points of folding the perfect paper plane. Check it out at the link in our bio.\n\xe2\x81\xa3'

b'Honored to help @rm_foundation @projecthopeorg @charitystars bring it home \xe2\x80\x94  and help the communities so many of our customers and crewmembers call home\xe2\x80\x94by flying critically needed PPE down to Puerto Rico for distribution in dozens of hospitals.'

b'Tee up the sweet tea, it\xe2\x80\x99s time to WFH (Wander From Home) to South Carolina. Our inflight partners will help you take in the sites, scroll down the streets and whip up some Southern treats. Fly over to the link in our bio and start wandering!'

b'Can\xe2\x80\x99t increase your altitude? You can still increase your aptitude! Introducing JetBlue Jr., a new educational video series designed to help kids learn about aviation (and hopefully, give grown-ups a much-needed break). Check out Lesson 1 \xe2\x80\x94 a nonstop course on air travel vocab featuring First Officer Sanaz \xe2\x80\x94 at the link in our bio now.'
b'Technically every day is Bring Your Kids To Work Day when you work from home. But it\xe2\x80\x99s still a day worth celebrating. #BringYourKidToWorkDay'

b'It\xe2\x80\x99s time to WFH (Wander From Home). We\xe2\x80\x99re transporting you to some of our favorite destinations with a little help from our partners. Ready to start wandering? Head to our Stories for a taste of Puerto Rico, courtesy of @food52 and @discoverpuertorico.'

b'Whether you\xe2\x80\x99re dreaming of the other side of the world or the other side of the house, we know many of you are in need of a getaway. Head to our story to see how our crewmembers are scratching the travel itch from home, and then show us how you #JetBlueFromHome.'
b'Whether you\xe2\x80\x99re a healthcare provider, essential worker, or doing your part by staying at home\xe2\x80\x94thank you. We can\xe2\x80\x99t wait to fly with you all again soon.'

b'Yesterday, we filled flight 226 from Tampa with respiratory devices donated by Mercury Medical, and flew them up to JFK for New York\xe2\x80\x99s hospitals. As New York\xe2\x80\x99s Hometown Airline, we are honored to help our city and state in the fight.'
